org.firstinspires.ftc.robotcore.external.hardware.camera

Interface SwitchableCamera

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Camera, CameraControls

    public interface SwitchableCamera
extends Camera
    SwitchableCamera allows one to control which camera on a switchable camera is in active at any given time.
    See Also:
    SwitchableCameraName, CameraManager.nameForSwitchableCamera(CameraName...)
